name: Crypto AI
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Crypto AI, an AI-powered using AI Machine Learning to Create Digital Asset.

What makes your project unique?
Two working product - AI Artist: https://cai.codes/artist and AI Chat - https://cai.codes/chat

History of your project.
Development of Image Diffusion trained to invert CLIP image embeddings. We finetuned SD 2.1 to accept a CLIP ViT-L/14 image embedding in addition to the text encodings. This means that the model can be used to produce image variations, but can also be combined with a text-to-image embedding prior to yield a full text-to-image model at 768x768 resolution.

What’s next for your project?
Development for AI Trading Analysis and more tools.

What can your token be used for?
Token can be use for future payment of premium plans to our api access.
